               <msContents>
                  <summary>Prayer of Moses which saved him from Pharoah, ጸሎተ፡ ሙሴ፡; Prayer when entering Battle; Prayer of David about Conflict, ጸሎተ፡ ዳዊት፡ በእንተ፡ ኵናት፡ ወፀብዕ፡; Anaphora of Our Lady Mary attributed to Cyriacus of Bǝhǝnsa, ቅዳሴ፡ ማርያም፡; Image of Saint George, መልክአ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡.</summary>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="1r" to="21v" facs="003">Fols 1r–21v</locus>
                     <title>Prayer of Moses which saved him from Pharoah, ጸሎተ፡ ሙሴ።</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>  ንነግረክሙ፡ ንሕነ፡ በዘድኅነ፡ ሙሴ፡ እምእዴሁ፡ ለፈርዖን፡ ጸሎት፡ ወስእለት፡ ለሙሴ፡ ዘወሀቦ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡</incipit>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <locus from="21v" to="22v" facs="024">Fols 21v–22v</locus>
                     <title>Prayer when entering battle</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">ወሶበ፡ ትበውእ፡ ውስተ፡ ቀትል፡ አንብብ፡ ዘንተ፡ ጸሎተ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/>
                     </incipit>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3">
                     <locus from="22v" to="24v" facs="025">Fols 22v–24v</locus>
                     <title>Prayer of David about Conflict, ጸሎተ፡ ዳዊት፡ በእንተ፡ ኵናት፡ ወፀብዕ።</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">ጸሎተ፡ ዳዊት፡ በእንተ፡ ኵናት፡ ወፀብዕ፡ ዘምሥራቅ፡</incipit>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i4">
                     <locus from="27r" to="57v" facs="029">Fols 27r–57v</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1099Anapho">ʾAkkʷateta qʷǝrbān
                                                  za-qǝddus Hǝryāqos za-hagara Bǝhnǝsā</title>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i5">
                     <locus from="59r" to="63v" facs="061">Fols 59r–63v</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2927RepCh208">Malkǝʾ-hymn to St
                                                  George</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">ሰላም፡ ለጽንሰትከ፡ ወለልደትከ፡ ቡሩክ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
